{"id": 3845, "title": "Ticket #3845: Param system ignoring per-daemon overrides", "description": "<blockquote>\nIt was discovered and fixed that the param system was ignoring per daemon overrides see ticket <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3822\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3822'); return false;\" title=\"param substitution does not honor per-daemon overrides\">#3822</a></span>. We want to add a test to test this out to avoid futures issues happening without detection. It was also discovered that a daemon specific override which referenced  a previous define could lead to an infinate loop of parsing. This example from ticket <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3822\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3822'); return false;\" title=\"param substitution does not honor per-daemon overrides\">#3822</a></span> was added as a third check\nmaking a total of 4 including the first check which simply tests for a job being\nable to run with the starting configuration.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2013-Aug-19 12:13:22 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nbe sure to have a test for self reference <div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">SCHEDD.FOO = $(FOO), bar</pre></div>\n. see <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3822\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3822'); return false;\" title=\"param substitution does not honor per-daemon overrides\">#3822</a></span>.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Aug-29 08:45</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/0da8bf19e4822ea3fa1d9890e214a0b0c7c98bb3\">[37410]</a></span>: This is really the one with the third check for the case where we evaluate params in an infinate loop <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3845\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3845'); return false;\" title=\"Param system ignoring per-daemon overrides\">#3845</a></span>  (By Bill Taylor )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Aug-28 12:27</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/f6620485933dc26ce69599c794a2508549889a0e\">[37404]</a></span>: Add check for discovered infinate parsing loop when daemon specific param references a previously defined param. Done as documented in 3822 for test <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3845\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3845'); return false;\" title=\"Param system ignoring per-daemon overrides\">#3845</a></span>  (By Bill Taylor )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2013-Aug-16 12:57</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/3dbcb5aa02d8e3bf601a689e2b250b7a5c97b421\">[37257]</a></span>: A new test which starts to test config param setting with respect to daemon override values also. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3845\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3845'); return false;\" title=\"Param system ignoring per-daemon overrides\">#3845</a></span>  (By Bill Taylor )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2014-Aug-06 12:04", "status": "resolved", "created": "2013-Aug-09 14:34", "fixed_version": "2013-Aug-09 14:34", "broken_version": "", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "Tests", "assigned_to": "bt", "derived_from": "#3594", "creator": "bt", "rust": "", "customer_group": "chtc", "visibility": "public", "notify": "johnkn@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}